{
  "id": "RAW_48c22fbb",
  "title": "终于有国产模型支持「看图写代码」了：9 块 9 元包月的 Doubao‑Seed‑Code 实测",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247499562&idx=1&sn=85d698d48a7bc855b66720bed759ab7c",
  "date": "2025-11-12 16:01:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近三个月我有强烈的感受，我们离「彻底脱离Claude Code」已经越来越近了。&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">字节跳动刚发布的Doubao-Seed-Code模型，有点超乎我的预期。超预期的地方，并不是因为它</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\">的代码能力特别拔尖，而是因为它让我们第一次看到了国产模型补齐一个写代码的硬需求——&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">在低价包月的同时，支持多模态、支持看图写代码！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去几个月，国产编程模型的硬实力突飞猛进，但是 「从截图到代码」 更多是演示级能力，或是根本不具备。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次 Doubao‑Seed‑Code 把它做成了</span><strong data-start=\"287\" data-end=\"295\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">一等公民</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：支持把</span><strong data-start=\"299\" data-end=\"322\"><span leaf=\"\">UI 截图、Figma 导出、手绘草图</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">还原为真实代码，并且能做</span><strong data-start=\"341\" data-end=\"355\"><span leaf=\"\">视觉比对后的小步修复</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。这不是“更强的写代码”，而是</span><strong data-start=\"370\" data-end=\"394\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">补齐了国产编码模型一个长期缺位的刚需能力</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">省流版</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">1. 国产AI代码模型中，暂时唯一，支持多模态、<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">支持看图写代码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">2. 包月价格便宜，首月9.9元，续费也仅需40元人民币。（下面有二维码）</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">3. 写代码硬实力<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">尚可</span>，在国产模型第一梯队。但是真诚地说，它不是特别拔尖。比Claude Sonnet 4.5/Opus 4.1/Codex 是有些差距的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">4. 上下文长度256K</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">5. 广泛兼容主流的AI编程工具，包括Claude Code/Cursor/Cline/Codex CLI等等。由于它支持看图写代码，使用其他，我们会发现，它比不支持看图写代码的模型，更接近原生Claude Code。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">6.&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">如果你没有Claude Code，可以直接在TRAE(国内版）里使用Doubao-Seed-Code，好用</span>！ 以前TRAE(国内版) 最能打的模型是DeepSeek，没有“看图写代码”能力，开发的时候有诸多不便，现在可方便多了</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">下面我们进行实测。 我们主要在Claude Code的躯壳下使用Doubao-Seed-Code，测试它“<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">看图写代码</span>”能力，因为在当下的国产模型中，这个能力是独一无二的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">技术实力</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">根据字节官方提供的信息，Doubao-Seed-Code在</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">Terminal Bench、SWE-Bench-Verified-Openhands、Multi-SWE-Bench-Flash-Openhands</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">等主流测评集中表现出色，仅次于Sonnet4.5</span></p>\n   <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\"></ul>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-w=\"1080\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5916666666666667\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=77417f66&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXkTR6CNLSp0c1Cbu7AT9vWZ3bkQLxzRqdwuGHpEo8ua0msgMXrd4cL9s5ibKWxK9CuqIcSPAObTG8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Doubao-Seed-Code 与TRAE开发环境深度结合后，能更快、更准地解决问题，登顶了SWE-Bench Verified榜单。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015913\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7046296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3e933da1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHllKjpKWo0wWnXiapepkZmjbpGICsYEuQ6YBCPLYTM4wGz2tqLZw1aCFnFIZFc4tjUb35LWDY73ibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">如何使用</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 4 []\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">购买方式：长按扫码可以花9.9元试试，也就一杯瑞幸，约等于免费。</span></p>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015888\" data-ratio=\"1.0106382978723405\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"940\" style=\"width: 353px;height: 357px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f8a26794&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHllKjpKWo0wWnXiapepkZmjIsWJBjfpt2f4ythu7AEyOU9mqmCvibeKXpLcvaRo7Zk3TxyM0tJzTMQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">如果你不方便扫码，也可以点击「阅读全文」</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">得到API Key以后，如果我们要在Claude Code中使用，可以在Terminal中修改环境变量，再启动Claude Code即可</span></p>\n  <pre style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;text-align: left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><code data-lark-language=\"JSON\" data-wrap=\"true\"><p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p><ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul><pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"javascript\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">export</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL</span>=<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">https</span>:<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">//ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/compatible</span></span></code><br><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">export</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN</span>=&lt;改成你的<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">ARK</span>-<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">API</span>-<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">KEY</span>&gt;</span></code><br><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">export</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">ANTHROPIC_MODEL</span>=doubao-seed-code-preview-latest</span></code><br><br><code><span leaf=\"\">claude</span></code><br><br></pre><p></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">配置成功后，可以询问它是啥模型，发个图片考考它，验明真身。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015889\" data-ratio=\"0.4172043010752688\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1860\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a221cc3c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHllKjpKWo0wWnXiapepkZmj4cTLlckgmPclpicb9Hic9UjKEtkjKdIbbia1x1bCO4H5iaBMt5lSB8Zmzg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p></code><br></pre>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">实测1：复刻纪念碑谷3D场景</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">纪念碑谷是我喜欢的游戏，在网页当中做出来并不容易，不仅需要审美，还需要对物理引擎的理解，还需要3D建模能力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们试试让Doubao-Seed-Code完成。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先给出Prompt</span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"\"><code><span leaf=\"\">写一个《纪念碑谷》风格 的3D 可交互游戏界面，根据提供的参考图风格，来构建一个等距视角 (Isometric) 场景，并添加一个持续的动画效果（例如图中某个结构的旋转）以让它“动起来”，同时必须实现简单的用户操作（如使用&nbsp;</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">OrbitControls</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;让用户能用鼠标旋转和缩放镜头）。场景明亮，模型的形状、纹理细节丰富，游戏场景精美，光影效果精美。有不懂的和我沟通</span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">再给出参考截图，毕竟</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">Doubao-Seed-Code能“看图写代码”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015890\" data-ratio=\"0.5602455871066769\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2606\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0c166f2c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHllKjpKWo0wWnXiapepkZmj3OqYRrJuicCMsCm5OPsjPUJgrjsBCq3OezD3vG9YKUNbHSvxuB3xOfQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">开始工作</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015892\" data-ratio=\"0.6444444444444445\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f437636d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHllKjpKWo0wWnXiapepkZmjxgDrsmyNNzicHd0oLibjE22oJVriaHxYKWoa4LsElef1wHV8iavShxaJtw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一次完成！！我录制了视频，你看看这质感！我公司的设计师同学惊呆了。</span></p>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">不过有点小瑕疵：虽然它理解了控件结构、完成了3D建模，但它对原图的还原度不够，可能这个任务还是太难了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">本次任务，整体我给打75分。 （如果Claude Sonnet 4.5 是90分的话）。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">实测2：把草图变成现实</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在我的实际工作中，经常会遇到一个场景：和同事在白板上讨论产品设计、画成草图，然后想要把草图变成现实。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">既然Doubao-Seed-Code可以“看图写代码”，我们让它试试。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们在草稿纸上画了个点咖啡的小程序。纯手工制品。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015900\" data-ratio=\"1.489814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 392px;height: 584px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b2664f55&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHllKjpKWo0wWnXiapepkZmjdD7FjkKz0vSqDFwZQ3l0n0GXLfaNx05KY6OKK4gpU9dGn8crUHwLuQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015901\" data-ratio=\"1.3564814814814814\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 388px;height: 526px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ea75ed78&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHllKjpKWo0wWnXiapepkZmjEgHKNL2e0JzgErfHVZTN2jqSU6sv1zpryNiaLnFsE4icfZpElsuxnHWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">给出Prompt</span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"css\"><code><span leaf=\"\">我要绘制一个咖啡购买界面的微信小程序界面演示，这是绘制的首页和菜单界面，需要根据我的操作创建两个界面，一个是访问主页的首页，一个是点击菜单按钮后，进入的菜单页面，需要注意暗色填充，尽可能保证细节精美，可以适当的用<span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">svg</span>图片填充页面中的组件里，不需要实现功能，聚焦在页面演示，有不懂的地方和我确认</span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">开始工作</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015902\" data-ratio=\"0.7287037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bcff4388&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHllKjpKWo0wWnXiapepkZmj2AhwkG6ISb4FRibaMJDxKdg5icmCtd3nZdN0F7prT0lznFMbf1gPibAmg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">自习看看Doubao-Seed-Code的回复，我表示满意。</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">看得出来，这个模型视觉理解非常在线，注意到了多图交互的疑点，以及猜对了我的潦草笔记。</span></p>\n   <div style=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">对于我草稿图提到的内容，事无巨细，全部完成。对于我草稿纸没有提到的细节，它也勤勤恳恳做了补充和发挥。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">补充完细节需求后，一次成形。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">值得一提的是：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">在网页中，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">Doubao-Seed-Code</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">还精心绘制了SVG图！</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">这次任务我给到80分。扣分内容主要审美。虽然它完全实现了我的草稿图，但是审美实在是不够现代化。</span></p>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">实测3：通过截图，像素级复刻其他产品</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">在我们实际编码工作中，还有一种场景情况： 我们想要参考其他产品的设计，引入到自己的项目中。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">有了Doubao-Seed-Code的“看图写代码”，这事也可以做了。让我们试试。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">我很喜欢Grammarly的首页，简洁、高级。这是它的首页截图。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015903\" data-ratio=\"0.6777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=478bc821&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHllKjpKWo0wWnXiapepkZmj14aj3Y45G6EGeAP1YsQUa9yaG835UWibTGwY8VHKkEUjdsNAiaYjMzrw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">为截图补充一条简简单单的指令</span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"\"><code><span leaf=\"\">我需要你对参考图中的页面进行 1:1 复刻，需要具备全部的元素细节，做一个一模一样的页面，如果有缺失的图片，你画SVG来实现，尽量一样。</span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我特地强调了“缺失的图片，你画SVG来实现”</span></p>\n   <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">先看看它画的SVG，70分吧，很像原版LOGO</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015908\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0eae2186&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHllKjpKWo0wWnXiapepkZmjZcIoKkgkelMoq3QWoQlVsTHHeAwBRJcn6b6ecUeLeWGz5s0BwbJWCw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">这是整体的实现效果。我打75分。</span></p>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">怎么样，还不错吧？&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">期待你的反馈！</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "字节跳动 Doubao-Seed-Code 模型实测，它首次为国产 AI 编程模型补齐了低价包月多模态「看图写代码」的刚需能力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "字节跳动 Doubao-Seed-Code 模型实测，它首次为国产 AI 编程模型补齐了低价包月多模态「看图写代码」的刚需能力。",
  "summary": "文章详细评测了字节跳动新发布的 Doubao-Seed-Code 模型，强调其在国产 AI 编程模型中首次实现了低价包月（首月 9.9 元，续费 40 元）且支持多模态「看图写代码」的独有能力。通过复刻纪念碑谷 3D 场景、将手绘草图转换为微信小程序界面以及像素级复刻 Grammarly 首页等实际案例，文章展示了模型在 UI 生成和代码还原方面的表现，尤其肯定了其强大的视觉理解能力。尽管作者坦言其代码硬实力与顶尖国际模型（如 Claude Sonnet 4.5/Opus 4.1/Codex）仍有差距，但在 Terminal Bench、SWE-Bench 等主流测评中表现出色，并与 TRAE 开发环境深度结合后能更快更准解决问题。Doubao-Seed-Code 的出现，标志着国产 AI 编程模型在补齐刚需能力方面迈出了重要一步，为开发者提供了更经济实用的替代方案，使其离“彻底脱离 Claude Code”又近了一步。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Doubao-Seed-Code 首次为国产 AI 编程模型带来了低价包月、多模态“看图写代码”的刚需能力，填补了市场空白。",
      "explanation": "这是其最核心的差异化优势，解决了开发者在低成本下利用视觉输入生成代码的刚需，尤其强调了“一等公民”的地位，而非演示级能力，以首月 9.9 元的极具竞争力的价格提供。"
    },
    {
      "point": "模型在 UI 生成和代码还原方面表现出色，尤其在视觉理解方面“非常在线”，但通用代码硬实力与顶尖国际模型仍有差距。",
      "explanation": "通过纪念碑谷 3D 场景、手绘草图转小程序、像素级复刻 Grammarly 首页等实测案例，证明了其强大的视觉理解和 UI 代码生成能力，同时也客观指出了与 Claude Sonnet 4.5 等模型的差距，为用户提供了真实预期。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Doubao-Seed-Code 与主流 AI 编程工具广泛兼容，并与 TRAE 开发环境深度结合，显著提升了国内开发者的效率和便利性。",
      "explanation": "模型不仅可以通过环境变量在 Claude Code 等工具中使用，还与国内 TRAE 开发环境深度集成，补齐了 TRAE 此前缺失的“看图写代码”能力，极大地提升了国内开发者在实际项目中的工作流效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Doubao-Seed-Code 的推出是国产 AI 编程模型发展的重要里程碑，加速了国内技术生态摆脱对国际顶尖模型依赖的进程。",
      "explanation": "作为首个实现此关键能力的国产模型，它标志着中国 AI 编程技术在特定刚需领域取得了突破，为国内开发者提供了更具自主性和性价比的选择，推动了“彻底脱离 Claude Code”的目标实现。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
